	   <tr><td colspan=2>One of the best resist wrist items for pure casters... only better ones&nbsp;&nbsp;are the <a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=15824 target=_new>Cazicite Diamond Bracer</a> (crafted) and the <a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=12900 target=_new>Wristband Of Secrets</a> (from Aten Ha Ra in Vex Thal).  Depending on who this one drops from (unknown to this site as of 12/10/02), I'd imagine many resist-seeking casters are going to pay for the Cazicite Diamond Bracer.  Unless Blocks of Cazicite are insanely rare drops and this one is a somewhat 'easy' kill... doubtful, though.<br><br>Or, you could just buy a <a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=4671 target=_new>Velium Blue Diamond Bracelet</a> and save thousands upon thousands of platinum for one less MR, FR, PR and DR (1 more CR, though)... you don't get the AC or HP (still the same Mana), but now you can afford other items that have them.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Dec 10 03:36:11 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>-------------<br>Too many active characters to list, on multiple servers.</td></tr>
